catalog.Description: {"imageTR":"images/teamspreview/wu256.png", "teamRosterDescription": "Worchester United plays with heart and hustle! These gritty underdogs from England prove you dont need glitz to be champions. With their no-nonsense style, they'll surprise everyone and show that true winners come from the unlikeliest places!"}
Making the switch from hockey to football as a teenager, Stevens brings a fearless attitude developed on the ice, and puts his body on the line, every time.
Elite defending masterclasses are standard for James Wells. Silky, unfazed, and near unbeatable for pace, Wells is a defensive rock, a natural winner, and thrives under pressure.
A midfield engine, Williams is a motor-racing enthusiast but knows theres more to life than speed. Mark makes teams purr, keeping it simple with short, simple passes.
For Travis, football is played in the mind. A rapid dribbler who loves to nibble at the opposition, Travis winds up defenders into making a mistake, then punishes them for it.

{"imageTR":"images/teamspreview/ck256.png", "teamRosterDescription": "The Cereal Killers are here to crunch the competition! Armed with killer skills and spoonfuls of talent, they'll pour on the pressure with cornflake kicks and milk-splash passes. Don't expect them to play nicethey're hungry for victory!"}
Big Slick, Joe Fontana is a hit with teammates and the ladies. Opponents? Not so much. Heavy challenges and fast feet, Joe loves to leave an impression, often getting a booking.
A leader at the back, and a sweeper keeper at heart, James is flashy, loud, and loves playing mind games with attacking players.
Quick and confident, James prefers pace to dribbling, playing off the shoulder with killer runs that beg for an inch-perfect through ball. Get it wrong and you can be sure youll know about it.
Proud Scot Stewart a is tough, rough, midfield destroyer who takes no prisoners in the centre of the park. Shinpads? What are ye, soft?
With incredible reactions and a vice-like grip from working construction with his father as a boy, legend has it Steve hasn't dropped a football in his life. Rock-solid at the back.
Hailing from London, UK, Hughes is a managers dream. No nonsense defending and a strong all-round game, Doug is good in the tackle, holds the ball well, and leads when it matters.
Hailing from Texas, to Stancil football is entertainment. Slow paced but fast footed, with an even faster mind, Stancil loves to humiliate teams. Welcome to the rainbow flick rodeo, yall.
A role model to kids around the world, Alvarez overcame obstacles to become one of the best forwards in football, while fighting for issues close to his heart. All hail King Kenny.

{"imageTR":"images/teamspreview/nb256.png", "teamRosterDescription": "Get ready for explosive action with the New York Boomers! These powerhouse players deliver booming shots and thunderous tackles, driven by the Big Apples energy. With skyscraper-sized ambition, theyre set to shake up the competition!"}
Young but wise, Lee is the keepers keeper - quiet, strong, analytical, and a master of positioning. You dont need speed if youre already in the right place.
The worlds fastest defender, Jae Park often gives his opponents a head start just to make life interesting. Adored by fans, and tolerated by coaches, just dont ask him to tackle.
A midfield maestro, incredible with the ball at his feet and an uncanny ability to read the game. Bruce was born to evade a press and play a defence-splitting ball.
Using his low centre of gravity to twist and turn, Nodas devastating combo of pace and power leaves regularly leaves helpless defenders in a tangled heap on the grass.

{"imageTR":"images/teamspreview/fd256_2.png", "teamRosterDescription": "The Flaming Dragons bring the heat! This fiery squad lights up every match with blazing speed and fierce determination. Their dragon-like intensity and hunger for victory will scorch the competition and leave rivals in ashes!"}

{"imageTR":"images/teamspreview/fcutrechtUnlock.png", "teamRosterDescription": "From the Netherlands, FC Utrecht brings Dutch precision and fearless play to the field! With rock-solid defense and game-changing moves, they keep fans on the edge. When Utrechts in action, expect thrilling and intense matches!"}
The Dutch Devil, de Keijzer rules his box with incredible power and athleticism, inspiring fear in opposing teams. Famous for spectacular dives and lightning reflexes.
The big brother of the squad and a team player through and through, softly spoken Mike prefers to listen to his teammates, support them, and do his talking on the pitch.
A Swiss army knife in the middle of the park, Ramselaars versatility means he can play any position and thrive, even between the posts if necessary.
A strong, aggressive attacker, Tasos lives for roaring crowds flashing cameras. A superstar in waiting and he knows it, Tasos won't let anyone stand in the way of his dreams.
World Cup Winner. Icon. Legend. Del Piero is a devastating deep-lying forward whos seen, done, and won it all.
A wunderkind wizard with the ball - and the world - at his feet, Arat dazzles his opponents with his tricks, speed, skill, and accuracy. A bright future awaits.
